Package: DTMdemo
Type: Package
Title: Basic DTM-Density Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Christoph Weitkamp
Maintainer: Christoph Weitkamp <cweitka@mathematik.uni-goettingen.de>
Description: Implementation of basic tools for the estimation and analysis of DTM-densities as proposed in the paper "From Small Scales to Large Scales: Distance-to-Measure Density based Geometric Analysis of Complex Data" (see https://arxiv.org/abs/2205.07689).
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: TDA (>= 1.8.7)
Imports: Rdpack (>= 0.7), stats (>= 4.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
RdMacros: Rdpack
